|               |       Projection: customer.c_custkey, customer.c_name, customer.c_address, customer.c_phone, customer.c_acctbal, customer.c_comment, lineitem.l_extendedprice, lineitem.l_discount, nation.n_name                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
